    <node id="Spanish Market Expansion">
      <data key="d0">Spanish Market Expansion</data>
      <data key="d1">event</data>
      <data key="d2">The Spanish market expansion is a TechNova initiative announced in Q4 2023, on which Jorge Ferreira and Lucas Pereira collaborate.&lt;SEP&gt;TechNova's 2024 initiative to expand into the Spanish market, led by Jorge Ferreira, targeting 3 enterprise clients.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-26b70bcb25c48c30ce81c6a5c453d7ec&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9049a6def58666ef149896d797cc954e</data>
