      <data key="d0">ML Pipeline Module</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">The ML pipeline module is a new component included in Orion v3.0, added to RetailCo's contract and scheduled for May 2024.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-26b70bcb25c48c30ce81c6a5c453d7ec</data>
