    <node id="Orion Platform">
      <data key="d0">Orion Platform</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">The Orion Platform is TechNova's primary product, launched in March 2023, with releases v1.0, v1.5, and v2.0, and a planned v3.0 with an embedded ML pipeline in May 2024.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-9049a6def58666ef149896d797cc954e</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1776799418</data>
