    <node id="EU AI Act">
      <data key="d0">EU AI Act</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The EU AI Act is a European Union regulation, specifically Article 13, with which three clauses in the GlobalBank contract were flagged as potentially non-compliant.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-9049a6def58666ef149896d797cc954e</data>
